              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma rays were detected using GRETINA array.",
                "GRETINA consists of 28 highly segmented coaxial",
                "germanium crystals. Each crystal is segmented into 36",
                "electrically isolated elements and four crystals are",
                "combined in a single cryostat to form a quad-crystal",
                "module. In present experiment 8 detctor modules were",
                "used."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons were detected using LENDA array of 24",
                "plastic scintillator bars with dimensions 300 x 45 x",
                "25 mm3. Each bar is read out by two PM tubes. Array",
                "is located at a distance of 1 m from reaction target.",
                "Energy is determined by time of flight. Neutrons with",
                "energies 150 keV to 10 MeV can be detected with high",
                "efficiency."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coincidencce between LENDA and GRETINA arrays",
                "was required"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Stable 24Mg beam with an intensity of 60 pnA at 170",
                "MeV/A impinged on a 1904 mg/cm2 thick 9Be production",
                "target at the entrance of the A1900 fragment",
                "separator. Resulting beam was purified in A1900",
                "resulting ina 23Al beam with purity of 13%. and",
                "intensity 8E+3 particles/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
